哈维尔·巴登不想见到梅南德斯兄弟并“与凶手坐在一起” https://www.nme.com/news/tv/javier-bardem-didnt-want-to-meet-the-menendez-brothers-and-sit-down-with-murderers-3815211?utm _source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=哈维尔-巴登不想见梅内德斯兄弟并与凶手坐下来Chris EdwardsFri, 22 Nov 2024 19:35:20 +0000 NewsTV NewsNetflix https://www.nme.com/?p=3815211 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Javier-Bardem.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Javier-Bardem.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Javier-Bardem-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Javier-Bardem-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Javier-Bardem-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Javier-Bardem-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Javier-Bardem-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位演员在 Netflix 的《怪物：莱尔和埃里克·梅南德斯的故事》中饰演他们的父亲</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/javier-bardem-didnt-want-to-meet-the-menendez-brothers-and-sit-down-with-murderers-3815211">哈维尔·巴登（Javier Bardem）不想见到梅南德斯兄弟并“与凶手坐下来”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Javier-Bardem.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Javier-Bardem.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Javier-Bardem-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Javier-Bardem-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Javier-Bardem-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Javier-Bardem-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Javier-Bardem-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/javier-bardem">哈维尔·巴登</a>透露，他不想见到梅南德斯兄弟，因为他无法“与凶手坐在一起”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/ryan-murphy-american-horror-story-the-politician-2690072">瑞恩·墨菲的美国成功故事：这位多产的制片人如何成为电视创意主脑</a></strong></li></ul><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/netflix">Netflix</a>的<em>《怪物：莱尔和埃里克·梅南德斯的故事》</em>中，巴登饰演兄弟俩遭受性虐待的父亲何塞。莱尔（尼古拉斯·亚历山大·查韦斯饰）和埃里克（库珀·科赫饰）因 1989 年谋杀何塞及其母亲基蒂（科洛·塞维尼饰）而被判无期徒刑，目前正在服无期徒刑。</p><p>巴登表示，在拍摄该剧时，他特别关注查韦斯和科赫，以确保他们不会让项目的黑暗吞噬他们。</p><p> “在旅程开始时，我说，‘伙计们，让我们提醒自己……并试着记住我们是被爱的，我们有真正关心我们、尊重我们的家人，他们爱我们，还有我们所爱的人。迫不及待地想回去，因为我们爱他们。”巴登在接受<a href="https://variety.com/2024/tv/columns/javier-bardem-monsters-menendez-brothers-dune-3-spellbound-1236217362/"><em>Variety</em></a>采访时回忆道。</p><p> “‘让我们来玩这个故事对我们作为演员的要求的游戏吧。但我们不要忘记这是一场游戏。这是虚构的。我不会以任何方式将我自己的任何东西放入其中，并且我不希望我做或说一些你可能期望的事情，因为它是写的，但有时也可能没有写或解决在笔记上，这可能会发生，请不要认为这是针对个人的。这是何塞、基蒂、埃里克和莱尔。” </p><figure id="attachment_3797376" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3797376" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3797376" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Javier-Bardem-Cooper-Koch-Nicholas-Chavez-Ryan-Murphy-and-Chloe-Sevigny-Photo-by-Gregg-DeGuire_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="《怪兽》演员阵容" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Javier-Bardem-Cooper-Koch-Nicholas-Chavez-Ryan-Murphy-and-Chloe-Sevigny-Photo-by-Gregg-DeGuire_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Javier-Bardem-Cooper-Koch-Nicholas-Chavez-Ryan-Murphy-and-Chloe-Sevigny-Photo-by-Gregg-DeGuire_Variety-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Javier-Bardem-Cooper-Koch-Nicholas-Chavez-Ryan-Murphy-and-Chloe-Sevigny-Photo-by-Gregg-DeGuire_Variety-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/upload